The Tubular Geodesics plugins were developed several years ago for [[Simple Neurite Tracer]] but remain functional in modern [[SNT]]. They can be installed manually as an SNT add-on. Once installed, they allow you to trace on a filtered-version of your image in which neuronal processes (and other tubular structures are significantly enhanced using [[ITK]] segmentation. More details on the following pages:

